\sum_{k=0}^{10} k = 0 + 1 + 2 + 3 + 4 + + 6 + 7 + 8 + 9 + 10
= 0 + 10 + 1+9 + 2+ 8+ 3 + 7+4+6+ 5 
 = 5 \cdot 10 + 5 = 55= \frac{10(10+1)}{2}
\sum_{k=0}^{11} k = 0 + 1 + 2 + 3 + 4 + + 6 + 7 + 8 + 9 + 10 + 11 
= 11 +0 + 10 + 1+9 + 2+ 8+ 3 + 7+4+6+ 5 
 = 6 \cdot 11 = 66 = \frac{11(11+1)}{2}
